title.rendered: Luann De Lesseps, Selena Gomez, Kendra Wilkinson & More: Star Sightings 12.07.2015

content.rendered:
There was a lot going on this past weekend. 

While most of us were kicking off the beer belly holiday season, some of your favorite stars were posing for photos on step-and-repeats, kicking a ball around for giggles or posing alongside Snoopy in the name of publicity.

Alrighty, who’s doing what?
